529
00:33:16,296 --> 00:33:17,380
Zrobić to?

530
00:33:33,546 --> 00:33:35,505
Dojechaliśmy do Café Gulshan.

531
00:33:38,880 --> 00:33:39,963
Ile?

532
00:33:40,463 --> 00:33:42,546
